# IRB Loss Given Default Categories

## identifier
dm427

## type
string

## definition
This dimension categorises information reported under the internal ratings-based (IRB) approach to credit risk, based on the loss given default category of an exposure, as determined in accordance with relevant prudential standards.

## codes
| Code                                           | Description                                          |
| ---------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------- |
| ClaimsSecuredByCommercialResidentialRealEstate | Claims Secured By Commercial Residential Real Estate |
| ClaimsSecuredByEligibleFinancialCollateral     | Claims Secured By Eligible Financial Collateral      |
